sequenceDiagram
    participant T as TelemetryIngest
    participant P as Planner
    participant R as Risk
    participant C as CarrierLookup
    participant O as RouteOptimizer
    participant V as Validator
    participant E as Execution
    participant A as Audit
    participant Reg as ToolRegistry

    T->>P: alert (TelemetryAlert)
    P->>P: provider.plan(alert)
    P->>R: state (plan_rationale attached)
    R->>Reg: call("risk_scorer", args)
    Reg-->>R: RiskAssessment
    R->>C: state (risk_assessment attached)
    C->>Reg: call("carrier_lookup", args)
    Reg-->>C: list[Carrier] or error
    Note over C: retries up to max_retries_carrier_lookup on error
    C->>O: state (candidate_carriers attached)
    O->>Reg: call("route_optimizer", args)
    Reg-->>O: (chosen_route, rejected_alternatives)
    O->>V: state (candidate_route attached)
    V->>Reg: call("route_validator", args)
    Reg-->>V: ValidationResult
    V->>E: state (validation_result attached)
    E->>Reg: call("execution_simulator", args)
    Reg-->>E: ExecutionResult or transient error
    Note over E: retries up to max_retries_execution on transient error
    E->>A: state (execution_result attached)
    A->>A: write AuditRecord to reports/audit_logs/
    A-->>T: final_status = SUCCESS
